mister x ( russian : мистер икс ) is a russian musical comedy film directed by yuliy khmelnitsky and based on the leningrad theatre of musical comedy operetta of the same name from 1956 .   the operetta itself was a russian adaptation of emmerich kálmán 's die zirkusprinzessin .   filming began in 1957 , with many of the actors and artists from the leningrad theatre working on the film as well .   it premiered in the soviet union and other countries on the may 2nd , 1958 .